title: Fix .gitignore + release workflow conflict for dist/
description: Workflow's 'git add dist' failed in CI because dist/ was in .gitignore. Removed dist/ from .gitignore so workflow can stage built output. Manually published pm-todos@2026.5.26 to npm to align with the other 16 pm-* packages released today.
